    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《任务时间》是一款综艺节目灵感的多人派对游戏，最多支持 8 名好友在 6 轮不可预测的任务和物理混乱中激烈角逐，争夺排行榜的冠军。由曾参与《萌萌小人大乱斗》和《糖豆人》的开发者打造的全新“友情大乱斗”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182680/extras/22db9d52dd283839bda08f4683cd26f2.poster.avif?t=1771344740\" width=1000 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182680/extras/22db9d52dd283839bda08f4683cd26f2.webm?t=1771344740\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182680/extras/22db9d52dd283839bda08f4683cd26f2.mp4?t=1771344740\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冲进一片无拘无束的混乱中，完成各种疯狂任务：你可以把朋友缩小、偷走他们的道具，然后眼睁睁看着他们掉进岩浆！你可能赢得胜利，也可能彻底玩脱，但请放心（大概）不会有现实后果。在这里，从来没有公平可言，而这正是游戏的乐趣所在。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《任务时间》上手简单，却难以精通，超过 50 万种随机任务组合，保证每一局都不一样，根本停不下来！就算是最手残的玩家，也能上演荒诞又精彩的逆转。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论你选择搞破坏、拼生存，还是单纯整蛊，《任务时间》都能带来一连串的爆笑时刻，考验的不只是友情，可能还有理智！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182680/extras/e2dcdcd93308c84337d25c3e4cd54267.poster.avif?t=1771344740\" width=1000 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182680/extras/e2dcdcd93308c84337d25c3e4cd54267.webm?t=1771344740\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182680/extras/e2dcdcd93308c84337d25c3e4cd54267.mp4?t=1771344740\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >综艺节目式的友情竞技场：<strong>6 轮混乱之后</strong>，只有一位玩家能加冕“<strong>终极任务者</strong>”。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >释放你内心的<strong>捣蛋鬼</strong>，疯狂整蛊对手——放心，现实中不会有后果，只有<strong>好心情和笑翻天的瞬间</strong>。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >上手容易，<strong>根本停不下来</strong>——每一轮都有逆袭机会，哪怕是最笨手笨脚的玩家也能爆冷获胜。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过 <strong>500 种可解锁的装扮与表情</strong>！最重要的是——<strong>绝无内购！</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50 万种以上的<strong>随机任务</strong>，带来<strong>无限可玩性</strong>。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持最多 <strong>8 人联机大厅</strong>，<strong>线上与 4 人分屏</strong>可以同时游玩。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多张<strong>活力十足的地图</strong>等待探索，充满<strong>互动道具与机关</strong>……而且未来还有更多！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >内置<strong>双语支持</strong>，专为直播设计——尽管开播，把欢乐传到中国或巴西的朋友们那里吧！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >来自全明星独立游戏团队，成员曾参与开发《萌萌小人大乱斗》、《糖豆人》等热门作品。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182680/extras/507c6325d3667d3fcf743f090b9823a9.poster.avif?t=1771344740\" width=1000 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182680/extras/507c6325d3667d3fcf743f090b9823a9.webm?t=1771344740\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182680/extras/507c6325d3667d3fcf743f090b9823a9.mp4?t=1771344740\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
